    "updated_at": "2012-01-04T18:48:34Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I think it makes sense to load config from the package every time, so its easily updatable. But we should probably also offer a simple mechanism to make a local copy of a package profile, so that the user can modify it.\n"
